token_lists.title: Green Comet
token_lists.description:
"Where Do We Come From? What Are We? Where Are We Going?"  - Paul Gauguin

The "Green Comet" passed very close to Earth again. This comet last appeared 50,000 years ago. The new Comet C/2022 E3 (ZTF) discovered some time ago is called the 'Green Comet'. This comet passed near our planet between February 1, 2023 and February 2, 2023.

token_lists.title: Simple_Syrup_230214
token_lists.description:
Simple_Syrup_230214 is a collection of 18 editions released to coincide with the gallery showing of editions 1, 2, and 3 at the Gerrard Art Space Gallery in Toronto, Canada. 

This collection is based on the original Simple_Syrup_1 on fxhash but with many new colour palettes and refinements.
